          "question": "Can I apply directly or do I really need a professional referral?",
          "answer": "You cannot apply directly — all applications must come through a referring agency or professional like a counselor, social worker, or senior center staff. Call 828-265-5434 ext. 139 to find approved referring agencies in your area."
