          "question": "What if the doctor won't complete the FL-2 form?",
          "answer": "The FL-2 form is required — without it, your parent cannot qualify. If their current doctor won't complete it, consider getting a second medical opinion or asking for a referral to a geriatrician who is familiar with these assessments."
